Hot Rod continued to fire on anything he saw moving outside the
Cybertronian Fire. He then thought about something, Prowl had left
during the fight. He opened his comlink, on Maximal frequincy's.
"Prowl. Prowl, do you read me? This is Hot Rod. Get back to the ship, we
still got Preds outfront. Can you hear me? Get you're ASS back to the
ship!"
He fired 3 shots at Scourge.
